[DhtmlXQ_comment0]eg xqsycj tjm 139 1h1c2a2e sw 1h2a2e 01||第139局 马炮士相全胜马士象全（一）||||This is one of the harder endgames. The key is NOT to exchange material with the weaker side or the game would quickly simplify to a draw. The opponent's advisor and elephants must be captured without loss in material.||There are 4 examples to this endgame situation.[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
